{{!--
{
  "layout": "standard",
  "title": "Vibes DIY | Build Something Special",
  "description": "Make a real web app just by describing it — live instantly, shared with a link, changed by talking to it. Read the blog, learn to build, and browse 760+ live example apps.",
  "ogUrl": "https://good.vibes.diy/",
  "source": "homepage"
}
--}}

<style>
        @import url('https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/alte-haas-grotesk');

        :root {
            --os-gray: #7A7A7A;
            --grid-gray: #CCCDC8;
            --goldenrod: #FEDD00;
            --ruby: #DA291C;
            --bluey: #009ACE;
            --ivory: #FFFFF0;
            --black: #231F20;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --forest: #2D7A4F;
            --violet: #6B3FA0;
            --grid-line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Alte Haas Grotesk', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--grid-gray);
            color: var(--black);
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        header {
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--grid-gray) 60%, transparent);
        }
        .logo-link { display: block; text-decoration: none; }
        .logo-img { height: 88px; width: auto; display: block; }

        /* ── Hero masthead ── */
        .index-hero {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 3rem 2rem 2rem;
        }
        .index-hero-inner {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--ivory);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 3.5rem 3rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .index-hero-inner::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
        }
        .hero-overline {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.3em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            opacity: 0.5;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        .index-hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6.5vw, 5rem);
            font-weight: bold;
            line-height: 1.0;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        .index-hero h1 .hi { color: var(--goldenrod); }
        .index-hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.75;
            max-width: 620px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .hero-badge-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        .hero-badge {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        /* ── Section structure ── */
        .index-section {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem 0;
        }
        .section-hdr {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.25em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--os-gray);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--black);
            padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        .section-hdr::before { content: "// "; }

        /* ── The three lanes ── */
        .lanes-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 900px) { .lanes-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
        .lane-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 18px;
            border: 3px solid var(--black);
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--black);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--black);
        }
        .lane-card:hover {
            transform: translate(-3px, -3px);
            box-shadow: 9px 9px 0 var(--black);
        }
        .lane-shot {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: top left;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--black);
            background: var(--black);
        }
        .lane-body {
            padding: 1.75rem 1.75rem 1.5rem;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .lane-kicker {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.68rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        }
        .lane-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        }
        .lane-card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #4a4a4a;
            line-height: 1.55;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .lane-cta {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 1.25rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .lane-blog    .lane-kicker, .lane-blog    .lane-cta { color: var(--bluey); }
        .lane-docs    .lane-kicker, .lane-docs    .lane-cta { color: var(--forest); }
        .lane-catalog .lane-kicker, .lane-catalog .lane-cta { color: var(--ruby); }

        .lane-sublinks {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 1.25rem 2rem 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .lane-sublinks .sub-label {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.68rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--os-gray);
            margin-right: 0.25rem;
        }
        .sub-chip {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 2px solid var(--black);
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--black);
            transition: background 0.15s ease;
        }
        .sub-chip:hover { background: var(--goldenrod); }

        /* ── Prose panel ── */
        .prose-panel {
            background: var(--ivory);
            border: 3px solid var(--black);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--black);
            padding: 2.5rem 2.75rem;
        }
        .prose-panel h2 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .prose-panel p {
            font-size: 1.02rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            max-width: 760px;
            margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
        }
        .prose-panel p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
        .prose-panel a { color: var(--bluey); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
        .prose-panel a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        /* ── Fun / Done / Alive ── */
        .triple-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 1.25rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 760px) { .triple-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
        .triple-cell {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 2px solid var(--black);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.75rem;
            box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }
        .triple-cell .cell-num {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            color: var(--os-gray);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .triple-cell h3 {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }
        .triple-cell p {
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            color: #4a4a4a;
            line-height: 1.55;
        }

        /* ── Two lanes: group chat / front counter ── */
        .two-lane {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1.25rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 760px) { .two-lane { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
        .lane-half {
            border: 3px solid var(--black);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 var(--black);
        }
        .lane-half.chat    { background: #fffde6; }
        .lane-half.counter { background: #e6f6ff; }
        .lane-half h3 {
            font-size: 1.45rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .lane-half > p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #4a4a4a;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .lane-half ul { list-style: none; }
        .lane-half li {
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            padding: 0.45rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .lane-half li strong { font-weight: 700; }

        .trust-strip {
            margin-top: 1.25rem;
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--ivory);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
            line-height: 1.65;
        }
        .trust-strip strong { color: var(--goldenrod); }

        /* ── Pull quote ── */
        .pull-quote {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem 2rem 0;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .pull-quote blockquote {
            font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.25rem);
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        .pull-quote .attribution {
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--os-gray);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 2rem 2rem;
            color: var(--os-gray);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        footer a { color: var(--os-gray); text-decoration: none; }
        footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        /* Newsletter */
        .newsletter-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem; }
        .newsletter-card { text-align: center; background: var(--ivory); border-radius: 20px; border: 3px solid var(--black); padding: 2.5rem; box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--black); }
        .newsletter-card h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        .newsletter-card > p { color: #555; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
        .newsletter-form { display: flex; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .newsletter-input { flex: 1; padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem; border: 2px solid var(--black); border-right: none; border-radius: 50px 0 0 50px; font-family: 'Alte Haas Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; background: var(--ivory); color: var(--black); outline: none; }
        .newsletter-input:focus { border-color: var(--bluey); }
        .newsletter-submit { padding: 0.9rem 1.75rem; background: var(--black); color: var(--ivory); border: 2px solid var(--black); border-radius: 0 50px 50px 0; font-family: 'Alte Haas Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; }
        .newsletter-submit:hover { background: var(--bluey); border-color: var(--bluey); }
        .newsletter-response { margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.875rem; min-height: 1.25em; }
        .newsletter-response.is-loading { color: var(--os-gray); }
        .newsletter-response.is-success { color: var(--bluey); }
        .newsletter-response.is-error { color: var(--ruby); }
        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .newsletter-form { flex-direction: column; }
            .newsletter-input { border-right: 2px solid var(--black); border-bottom: none; border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0; }
            .newsletter-submit { border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .index-hero-inner { padding: 2.5rem 1.75rem; }
            .prose-panel { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
        }
    </style>

<main>
    <!-- ── Hero masthead ── -->
    <section class="index-hero">
        <div class="index-hero-inner">
            <div class="hero-overline">GOOD.VIBES.DIY — THE VIBES SHOWCASE</div>
            <h1>Software is getting<br><span class="hi">weird</span> again.</h1>
            <p>Vibes lets you make a real web app just by describing it — it's live instantly, you share it with a link, and you keep changing it by talking to it. This site is the public record of what that looks like: the blog, the builder's docs, and a catalog of hundreds of live apps. Everything here is cloneable and yours.</p>
            <div class="hero-badge-row">
                <span class="hero-badge">760+ apps live</span>
                <span class="hero-badge">Takes orders</span>
                <span class="hero-badge">Remix anything</span>
                <span class="hero-badge">Open source</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── The three lanes ── -->
    <section class="index-section">
        <div class="section-hdr">Start Here</div>
        <div class="lanes-grid">

            <a href="blog/" class="lane-card lane-blog">
                <img class="lane-shot" src="images/blog/group-chat-to-front-counter/card.png" alt="Blog post card: from the group chat to the front counter" loading="lazy">
                <div class="lane-body">
                    <div class="lane-kicker">01 · Field Notes</div>
                    <h2>The Blog</h2>
                    <p>Dispatches from the build log — evals of the app generator, positioning notes, and engineering stories from a team shipping in public. Latest: every vibe just got a backend.</p>
                    <span class="lane-cta">Read the Blog →</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="creator-documentation/" class="lane-card lane-docs">
                <img class="lane-shot" src="images/screenshots/creator-documentation.jpg" alt="Creator documentation: build, script, and ship" loading="lazy">
                <div class="lane-body">
                    <div class="lane-kicker">02 · Build, Script, Ship</div>
                    <h2>Builder's Docs</h2>
                    <p>Guides for making a vibe of your own: prompt-to-app walkthroughs, the one-command CLI, connecting backend data, and the full sharing &amp; access reference. Every app on this site started from a prompt — these show you how.</p>
                    <span class="lane-cta">Read the Docs →</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="apps.html" class="lane-card lane-catalog">
                <img class="lane-shot" src="images/screenshots/group-ranker.jpg" alt="Group Ranker, one of the live app collections in the catalog" loading="lazy">
                <div class="lane-body">
                    <div class="lane-kicker">03 · The Gallery</div>
                    <h2>The App Catalog</h2>
                    <p>The full example gallery — live app collections, audience pages for teachers and food trucks, games and puzzles, and university-grounded edu clusters. Nothing here is a mockup. Open one, then remix it.</p>
                    <span class="lane-cta">Browse the Catalog →</span>
                </div>
            </a>

        </div>
        <div class="lane-sublinks">
            <span class="sub-label">Builder shortcuts:</span>
            <a class="sub-chip" href="generate.html">CLI: npx vibes-diy generate</a>
            <a class="sub-chip" href="sharing.html">Sharing &amp; Access</a>
            <a class="sub-chip" href="vibes-connect/">Vibes Connect</a>
            <a class="sub-chip" href="builders.html">For Builders</a>
            <a class="sub-chip" href="built.html">How It Gets Built</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── What is Vibes ── -->
    <section class="index-section">
        <div class="section-hdr">What Is Vibes DIY</div>
        <div class="prose-panel">
            <h2>Tiny software for your specific situation</h2>
            <p>Vibes DIY is for making tiny custom software — things built for your specific situation, your specific people. A trivia night for the group chat, or an order form for the shop. The same move either way: describe it, it's live at a link, and you keep changing it by talking to it. Nobody starts from a blank page, and nobody has to call themselves a coder.</p>
            <p>good.vibes.diy is the public gallery of what people are making with it. The <a href="apps.html">catalog</a> collects hundreds of live apps for their night, their league, their shop, their weird specific thing. Every one is deployed on the <a href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">Vibes DIY platform</a> — not a mockup, not a prototype. If you see something close to what you need, clone it and make it yours.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Fun, done, alive ── -->
    <section class="index-section">
        <div class="section-hdr">The Whole Pitch</div>
        <div class="triple-row">
            <div class="triple-cell">
                <div class="cell-num">01</div>
                <h3>Fun</h3>
                <p>Build for any reason, or no reason. A bit for the group chat, a game for the kids — or because the spreadsheet is killing you.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="triple-cell">
                <div class="cell-num">02</div>
                <h3>Done</h3>
                <p>It's a real app, live at its own link. Not a prototype. It takes the order the moment it's live — add a payment flow when you're ready.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="triple-cell">
                <div class="cell-num">03</div>
                <h3>Alive</h3>
                <p>Keep talking to it and it keeps changing. So can anyone you share it with — seeing a vibe makes you want to change it.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Two audiences, one move ── -->
    <section class="index-section">
        <div class="section-hdr">From the Group Chat to the Front Counter</div>
        <div class="two-lane">
            <div class="lane-half chat">
                <h3>The group chat</h3>
                <p>Friends, hobbies, a bit, a night out. Build for fun.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>The teacher</strong> remixes a flashcard vibe into a live trivia game — students change the questions mid-round.</li>
                    <li><strong>The car club</strong> shares one restoration log; everyone tracks their garage on the same tool.</li>
                    <li><strong>The group chat</strong> settles best-taco once and for all with a tier-list ranker everyone votes in.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="lane-half counter">
                <h3>The front counter</h3>
                <p>The taco truck, the contractor, the shop with a duct-taped spreadsheet. Build to get something done.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>The food truck</strong> posts a daily-specials board that takes the order the moment it's live.</li>
                    <li><strong>The contractor</strong> replaces texts and a clipboard with jobsite checklists and a customer portal.</li>
                    <li><strong>The shop</strong> turns the spreadsheet everyone fights over into a form, a dashboard, and one source of truth.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-strip">
            <strong>You control your app's data.</strong> A new vibe starts private to the people you invite — you choose who can read, write, and open it — and you publish it to the world when you're ready. It's all open source, so anyone can look under the hood.
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── The medium ── -->
    <section class="index-section">
        <div class="pull-quote">
            <blockquote>"Seeing should imply changing."</blockquote>
            <div class="attribution">The test for everything on this site</div>
        </div>
    </section>

{{> newsletter}}
</main>
